To have and to hold. Tiffany diamonds are sourced with care and consideration. In 2019, we enhanced our approach to transparency through our Diamond Source Initiative which shares with our customers the provenance—region or countries of origin—of all newly sourced, individually registered diamonds. Leave your resolutions below and discover more via the link in bio. #TiffanySustainability

Wild thing. We are proud to continue our commitment to protecting the earth through the #TiffanySaveTheWild collection by donating 100% of the profits to the Wildlife Conservation Network (@wildnetorg). Since the collection's launch in 2017, we have consistently exceeded our donation pledge and raised more than USD $5 million.
